public static enum RemoteUltrasonicPoller.USPState
extends java.lang.Enum<RemoteUltrasonicPoller.USPState>

The various modes of the ultrasonic poller

PING_CENTER - Pings only the center ultrasonic *

PING_ALL - Pings all the Ultrasonic sensors at the same time

PING_LEFT - Pings only the left ultrasonic

PING_RIGHT - Pings only the right ultrasonic

PING_SEQUENTIAL - Pings all the ultrasonic sensors, but only one at a time (each sensor is polled every 3 * pollRate

PING_SIDES - Pings only the two ultrasonic sensors on the sides, ignoring the center one.

Author:
Danielle
